ban add.description: Bans a member from your server.

ban remove.description: Unban a member from your server
ban remove.usage: `/ban remove [user] : [select from the list of banned members]`

timeout add.description: Timeout a member in your server

ticket setup.description: Setup tickets by Grabe_. in your server.
ticket setup.usage:
`/ticket setup
[description] : [Description for the ticket embed]
[footer] : [footer for the ticket embed]
[role1] : [1st role which will be pinged in the ticket]
[role2] : [2nd role which will be pinged in the ticket]
[role3] : [3rd role which will be pinged in the ticket]`

ticket embed.usage: `/ticket embed [channel] : [channel where the embed will be sent.]`

giveaway create.usage:
`/giveaway create
[time] : [for example 3 days]
[winners] : [amount of winners]
[channel] : [channel where the giveaway will be held]
[image] : [image for the giveaway (links only)]
[filtered_role] : [only the members with this role will be able to enter]`

giveaway end.description: End a ongoing giveaway if you're too impatient.

wanted.description: Sends a wanted poster using someones pfp.

roll.description: Rolls a dice with imaginary number of sides.

rps.description: Play rock-paper-scissor with the bot to get annihilated.

coinflip.description: Make the bot do a coinflip for you.

aiflip.description: Try guessing coinflip sides with the bot.

choose.description: Make the bot choose between two things for you.

gayr8.usage: `-gayr8 [member] : [the person's whose gayr8 will be displayed]`

simpr8.usage: `-simpr8 [member] : [the person's whose simpr8 will be displayed]`

joke.description: Sends a random dad joke from an api.

roast.description: Fucking shove a jcb truck in someone's asshole by roasting them.

whois.description: Shows some usefull information on a member.

avatar.usage: `/avatar [member] : [the member whose avatar will be displayed]`

poll create.usage:
`/poll create
[question] : [the question for the poll]
[options ...] : [the options for the poll]`

poll info.usage:
`/poll info
[channel] : [channel where the poll was held]
[ID] : [ID of the poll embed]`

remind.description: Make the bot remind you something on a certain time.

setnick.description: Change someone's nickname in your server.
setnick.usage:
`/setnick
[member] : [the member whose nickname will be changed]
[newnick] : [the new nickname]`

embed.description: Create and send embeds through the bot.
embed.usage:
`/embed
[channel] : [Where the embed will be sent]
[title] : [title of the embed]
[description] : [description of the embed]
[color] : [color of the embed]
[image] : [image for the embed (links only)]`

serverinfo.description: Get some really usefull info on servers.

channel access.description: Manage a user or bot's access to a channel.
channel access.usage:
`/channel access
[object] : [the member/bot]
[type] : [to add/remove access]
[channel] : [the channel where access will be edited]`

channel lockdown.description: Locks all the channels in the server.

role multiple.description: Add/Remove a role from multiple users.
role multiple.usage:
`/role multiple
[role] : [the role which will be added or removed]
[type] : [to add or remove]
[user_type] : [humans/bots/all]`

channel lock.description: Lock a channel and make it un-chatable.
channel lock.usage: `/channel lock [channel] : [the channel which will be locked]`

channel unlock.description: Unlock the channel and make it chatable.
channel unlock.usage: `/channel unlock [channel] : [the channel which will be unlocked]`

channel slowmode.usage:
`/channel slowmode
[time] : [for example 5seconds]
[channel] : [the channel where slowmode will be added]`

kick.description: Kick a member from your server.
kick.usage:
`/kick
[member] : [the member which you want to kick]
[reason] : [the reason for kicking this member]`

giveaway entries.description: Shows all the entries of a giveaway.

giveaway.description:
Grabe_.'s giveaway commands.
**SubCommands** : `/giveaway create` , `/giveaway entries` , `/giveaway end`
